AboutMe.TextAbout1: Hello! I am a full stack web developer, specialized in backend. I am 24 years old, from Argentina, and currently living in Buenos Aires.
AboutMe.TextAbout2: My journey in programming began when I successfully completed the Soy Henry bootcamp.
AboutMe.TextAbout3: I am very excited to showcase my knowledge and skills, and contribute to projects that I am passionate about.
